body:
Note that the eager APIs are NOT stable, so use at your own risk. They may change at any time (as we're experimenting with them) and we do not plan to restrict even trivial changes (like changing symbol names) to maintain compatibility at this time

With that disclaimer on the way, this is likely because [`version_script.lds`](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/c/version_script.lds) prunes out all the `TFE_*` symbols. You are welcome to send in a PR :)
